dc_description_s: This data layer represents roads for Portage County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase, 'Portage_Roads_2014'. [The Centerline data set is a vector representation of center of pavement in the County of Portage, Wisconsin. The centerlines are digitized from 1:12000 digital orthophotography or entered by coordinate geometry.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.
